| Feature                 | Implementation                                        |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| **Layered Encryption**  | AES-256-GCM + XOR obfuscation + PBKDF2 key derivation |
| **Hardware Binding**    | Session salts derived from safe hardware signatures   |
| **Runtime Obfuscation** | Strings encrypted as self-decrypting code             |
| **Tamper Detection**    | Checksums + sealed data with expiration               |
| **Memory Safety**       | Secure cleanup with `destroy()` method                |
| **Compression**         | LZW-style compression for configs/API keys            |




import { mangekyoCipher, StringVault } from './custom-encryption.js';

// Encrypt API key
const encrypted = await mangekyoCipher.encryptString(apiKey, userPassword);

// Runtime string protection (appears as random code)
const obfuscated = mangekyoCipher.runtimeObfuscate('sensitive_string');

// Vault storage
const vault = new StringVault(mangekyoCipher);
await vault.store('deepl_key', apiKey, password);